{"tid":1682672,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾意左個差佬... (求屌醒)","createTime":"2019-10-30T07:52:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T14:42:21.000Z","uid":89349,"like":201,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"61d84f491fdcffc76b50691885a6003e75f48a93","tid":1682672,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T07:52:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ae0PWob.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fae0PWob.png&h=0c662476&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">其實我都知呢班人壞事做盡，好快俾天收。。<br />\n但我都係忍唔住，愛上左一個差佬。。<br />\n我知佢有兩個女<br />\n一個叫宇晴。。。一個叫宇蕎</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">出來夜場玩，好少雞虫會提自己個女既名，所以我覺得佢都係一個顧家既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家有冇睇老豆搵仔呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我好似見到佢。。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"568c9066b521a68248e3247b56d5fed5bca2ad09","tid":1682672,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T07:53:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zSLXe8W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzSLXe8W.jpg&h=d3761788&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"df6cf8d3ae7ed01c53e2d9e8bcd68ec2ffd6ce30","tid":1682672,"uid":31200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T07:54:46.000Z","msg":"邊度轉貼架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cb3d81aff576533c9d312d734920129f30de1ee","tid":1682672,"uid":147916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:32:20.000Z","msg":"戇鳩同你講咗有女你仲會受？"},